  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK848">
<l>ēvavuñ ceykalāṉ ṟāṉṟēṟā ṉavvuyir </l>
<l>pōo maḷavumōr nōy</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The fool will not perform (his duties) even when advised nor ascertain them himself such a soul is a burden (to the earth) till it departs (from the body).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
